      "settings": {
        "sectionWidth": "container--large",
        "title": "",
        "titleTag": "h2",
        "details": "<p>Easy Peel Transfers are the evolution of hot peel transfers - combining everything you know and love about cold peel, combined with the benefits of hot peel such as time savings and easier peeling of fine details. <\/p><p>Easy Peel Technology is the latest innovation from Ninja Transfers, designed to revolutionize your apparel decorating experience. <strong>Easy Peel is the evolution of Hot Peel Transfers—combining everything you've wanted from Hot Peel while maintaining everything you've grown to love about Cold Peel.<\/strong> Now, you can peel your transfers <strong>2-4 times faster<\/strong>, saving you time and boosting your productivity. With the ability to <strong>peel hot or cool<\/strong>, these transfers make the peeling process faster and more efficient. Whether you're a seasoned professional or just starting out, Easy Peel Transfers make decorating apparel stunning, easier than ever.<\/p>",
        "paddingTop": 0,
        "paddingBottom": 80
      }
    },
